Profile missing values

Source: R/profile_missing.R
profile_missing.Rd

Analyze missing value profile

Usage

profile_missing(data)

Arguments

data

input data

Value

missing value profile, such as frequency, percentage and suggested action.

See also

plot_missing

Examples

profile_missing(airquality)
#>   feature num_missing pct_missing
#> 1   Ozone          37  0.24183007
#> 2 Solar.R           7  0.04575163
#> 3    Wind           0  0.00000000
#> 4    Temp           0  0.00000000
#> 5   Month           0  0.00000000
#> 6     Day           0  0.00000000
